1
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:41,000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,960
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:47,479
Just to do Bai Yongjun a favor.

4
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:49,880
After all, he highly recommended that guy.

5
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,170
Do you have someone in mind?

6
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:59,120
Look at this.

7
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:04,030
[Career Direction Assessment Report]

8
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:04,490
This person's assessment result
is quite impressive.

9
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:06,280
Born to work in the hotel industry.

10
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,540
A bright future ahead.

11
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:08,960
Who is this?

12
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:10,910
Xu Miyu.

13
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:16,560
This kind of assessment
is similar to MBTI.

14
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,310
It's just for reference.

15
00:02:17,310 --> 00:02:18,710
We shouldn't blindly trust it.

16
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:19,870
Besides, you should know

17
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:22,840
that cross-department transformation is
troublesome.

18
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,870
I can handle complicated procedures.

19
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,400
Now, what I'm not sure about is

20
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,530
whether my decision is too arbitrary.

21
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,190
What do you think, Rui?

22
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:32,000
Is Xu Miyu really capable of

23
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:34,190
being our lobby manager?

24
00:02:36,730 --> 00:02:39,160
I saw her performance earlier today.

25
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,100
[Purong Hotel]

26
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:42,310
She is as calm and resourceful as Anna.

27
00:02:42,310 --> 00:02:44,710
And she knows the hotel's situation
very well.

28
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:46,400
She is a very good candidate.

29
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,590
However,

30
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,280
I don't know Xu Miyu's opinion.

31
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,030
How about I talk to her?

32
00:02:55,970 --> 00:02:56,500
Okay.

33
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,360
Transfer me to the Front Office?

34
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,160
That's right.

35
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:15,300
This is our preliminary resolution.

36
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:18,240
It still needs to go through
a management vote.

37
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,430
Also, we need to consider
your personal wishes.

38
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:22,590
So, I came to talk to you first today.

39
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:24,210
Are you willing to?

40
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,630
Thank you.

41
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,320
Director Bai.

42
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,630
Ms. An started her maternity leave
ahead of schedule yesterday.

43
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,160
You know about this, right?

44
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,280
So, now, in the Front Office,

45
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,480
a lobby manager position has opened up.

46
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:47,520
The leaders attach great importance
to this matter.

47
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,590
After discussing it with
the HR Department,

48
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:52,190
they've decided to assign
a new lobby manager.

49
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:55,650
Why do they need to send someone over?

50
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,310
Who is it?

51
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,800
Has the candidate been decided?

52
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,430
It hasn't been finalized yet.

53
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:02,750
It's just a pending candidate.

54
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:07,740
I want to know

55
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,280
why you chose me.

56
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:12,170
Do you remember this test?

57
00:04:13,140 --> 00:04:15,410
[Controlling][Influential][Strict][Calm]

58
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,750
According to the report,

59
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,190
in the aspects of image,

60
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:19,250
communication skills, and loyalty,

61
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,269
you are stronger than

62
00:04:21,269 --> 00:04:22,870
other candidates

63
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,130
for the lobby manager.

64
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,830
What do you think?

65
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,270
Do you have any concerns?

66
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,870
I have a concern.

67
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,120
Is it because you are my friends

68
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:40,480
and you are overestimating me?

69
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:41,570
Mr. Xue,

70
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,690
to be honest, recently,

71
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,830
I indeed felt a bit confused about

72
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,190
my career planning.

73
00:04:47,409 --> 00:04:49,490
That is why I took this evaluation.

74
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,960
If I say I don't want to get promoted,

75
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,190
it will be a lie.

76
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,510
Today, knowing that

77
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:56,110
I have so many possibilities,

78
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:58,280
and could even become a lobby manager,

79
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,120
I am truly happy.

80
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,750
I also wish I could tell you

81
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,020
that I'm willing to give it a try.

82
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:05,220
However,

83
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:07,310
this is a cross-departmental promotion
after all.

84
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:09,610
Besides, I'm far from familiar with

85
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,510
the front desk work.

86
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,480
I think

87
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,210
you trust me unconditionally,

88
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:17,120
because you guys are my friends.

89
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,130
But also, for that reason,

90
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,600
I'm even more afraid of

91
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:22,630
letting you down.

92
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,040
Forewoman of the executive floor?

93
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,600
Xu Miyu, the one
who always flatters the leader?

94
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,460
Director Bai, you freaked me out.

95
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,920
Subordinates are spreading rumors.

96
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,780
But we shouldn't join in the fuss.

97
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,240
Ms. Xu is exceptionally capable

98
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,560
in her work.

99
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:39,320
In the opening of the Chinese restaurant

100
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,750
and Ms. An's emergency yesterday,

101
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:43,040
she was at the front line

102
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,600
and did an excellent job.

103
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,310
It's obvious to everyone.

104
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:57,070
Did the HSKP Department kick her out

105
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:59,070
and shove her into the Front Office?

106
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:01,000
She's just a forewoman.

107
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,000
How could she be a lobby manager?

108
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:05,680
When promoting someone,

109
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,950
we need to emphasize person-job fit.

110
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,630
Not to mention that the lobby manager,

111
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:11,160
who is the face of our hotel.

112
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:12,430
It connects upwards to
the general manager

113
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:15,290
and downwards to
every department and every guest.

114
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:18,190
You guys found such an ass-kisser
to fool me?

115
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:19,280
Your tricks are

116
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,720
too blatant.

117
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,100
Xu Miyu.

118
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:24,490
I'm sitting here

119
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,680
not to represent Mr. Ji and myself,

120
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,050
but for the interests of Purong Hotel.

121
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,040
Meanwhile, since we are friends,

122
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,950
we will not put you

123
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,320
in an unsuitable position,

124
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,760
letting you bear

125
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:38,520
undue pressure and criticism.

126
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:40,480
Just as we believe in you,

127
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,440
we hope you can believe in us,

128
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,720
and more importantly, in yourself.

129
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:48,390
I understand, Mr. Xue.

130
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,120
May I ask

131
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:53,500
who recommended me?

132
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:55,440
Is the answer that important?

133
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,440
It was Mr. Ji himself.

134
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,560
If you really

135
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,220
don't know where your path is,

136
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,820
you might as well start with
trial and error.

137
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,540
Step out of your comfort zone

138
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:21,440
and see the other sides of that iceberg.

139
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,750
♪ Bury everything in your mind ♪

140
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:24,110
Meeting guests' needs
is your responsibility,

141
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,790
while supporting you is mine.

142
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,550
♪ Hope love blossoms as wished ♪

143
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,140
I'm your boss.

144
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,980
I will be responsible for you.

145
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:31,940
♪ Rainwater silently nourishes flowers ♪

146
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,820
You can trust me a little more,

147
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:32,500
okay?

148
00:07:33,570 --> 00:07:34,550
♪ At its own expense ♪

149
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:38,150
In the past,
when faced with things I wanted,

150
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:38,590
♪ In the hot summer ♪

151
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,480
I was always used to putting in

152
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,560
a little more effort than others,

153
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:42,670
♪ I'm melting ♪

154
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:45,010
cautiously pleasing others and weighing

155
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:48,750
♪ Before the flowers wither,
I pretend to be cool ♪

156
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,650
just to prove that I deserved
to have them.

157
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:51,650
But now he keeps telling me

158
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:51,870
♪  Ah  ♪

159
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,800
that everyone in this world

160
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:55,950
♪Talking to myself♪

161
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,800
is a shining star.

162
00:07:56,970 --> 00:07:59,810
I can be seen without trying to
please others.

163
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,850
♪Ah♪

164
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:04,080
♪ Though I'm alone,
I pretend to be at ease ♪

165
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:04,190
I deserve to be firmly chosen
without having to prove myself.

166
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:07,300
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

167
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,720
[Chapter 2: Project Management Process]

168
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:09,840
[Chapter 3: Project Activation]

169
00:08:08,210 --> 00:08:11,160
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

170
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:11,350
For you, moving from the HSKP Department
to the Front Office,

171
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:11,020
[Project Selection and Feasibility Study]

172
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:12,750
in terms of specific work content,

173
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:15,100
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

174
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:15,410
you will face new challenges
and difficulties.

175
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,160
You need to get prepared.

176
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:18,900
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

177
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,400
As for any other problems,

178
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:20,870
don't worry.

179
00:08:20,090 --> 00:08:22,290
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

180
00:08:20,590 --> 00:08:24,900
[Project Selection and Feasibility Study]

181
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,730
Leave them to Mr. Ji and me.

182
00:08:22,930 --> 00:08:25,120
I will work hard not to let you down.

183
00:08:23,170 --> 00:08:25,980
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

184
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:29,480
Xu Miyu, do you remember what I told you

185
00:08:27,010 --> 00:08:30,090
♪ Questions without answers ♪

186
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,920
in your interview?

187
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,720
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

188
00:08:32,789 --> 00:08:34,360
Purong Hotel will provide everyone

189
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,909
who has career aspirations

190
00:08:35,179 --> 00:08:36,720
♪ Let them go ♪

191
00:08:35,909 --> 00:08:38,390
with a matching path for promotion.

192
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:41,770
So, you should believe in yourself.

193
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:43,010
One day,

194
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:46,260
you will definitely become
an excellent hotel worker.

195
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,440
Your clothes have been washed.

196
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,130
Thank you.

197
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:12,480
Do you need anything else?

198
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,240
No.

199
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:17,380
Hello.
Here is the mineral water you asked for.

200
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:17,940
Thank you.

201
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,240
Do you need anything else?

202
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,030
No.

203
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,270
Room service.

204
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,540
-Sorry, sir.
-Get it right next time.

205
00:09:51,610 --> 00:09:52,730
It's you.

206
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,800
Miyu.

207
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,000
No need, no need.

208
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,930
I made the bed myself this morning.

209
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,870
Then, I'll go outside.

210
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,000
Listen, Miyu.

211
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,240
The floor is perfectly clean.

212
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,170
You don't need to clean it anymore.

213
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,630
Can you please

214
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,510
stop doing one chore after another?

215
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,120
Come here.

216
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:32,080
Sit down and chat with me.

217
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,600
Daniel, I am your butler first,

218
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,170
and then, your friend.

219
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:38,470
Taking care of your daily life is my job.

220
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,960
You have to let me finish my work first.

221
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,600
No problem.

222
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,200
Leave the work for tomorrow.

223
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:46,600
It might not be me tomorrow.

224
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:48,840
What?

225
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,920
Is someone trying to fire you again?

226
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:53,960
Tell me.

227
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,290
I'll tell the Old Madam.

228
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:57,760
Let's see who dares to bully you again.

229
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,760
This is too much.

230
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:01,060
You mean when I was about to be fired,

231
00:11:01,090 --> 00:11:03,090
Aunt Wanjun helped me?

232
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,190
Chairman Wei.

233
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:12,240
Why so distant?

234
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:13,940
For what happened before,

235
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,960
thank you.

236
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,750
There's nothing to be embarrassed about.

237
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:19,480
She is your chairwoman,

238
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,000
your Aunt Wanjun,

239
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,510
and also my cousin Wanjun.

240
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,200
Who is your cousin?

241
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,500
You old fool.

242
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:27,870
By the way.

243
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:30,070
Miyu, let's continue where we left off.

244
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:32,580
Who wronged you again?

245
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,370
You'd better tell us

246
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,520
everything.

247
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:37,510
Your chairwoman will stand up for you.

248
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,320
Actually,

249
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,390
I wasn't wronged,

250
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,390
and I don't need anyone to
stand up for me.

251
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,360
It's just that

252
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:47,150
I'm going to be the lobby manager
at the Front Office.

253
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:49,140
You got a promotion!

254
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:51,910
That's great news.

255
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,630
Why didn't you tell me just now?

256
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,360
You made me worry for nothing.

257
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,000
I'm sweating.

258
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,240
I am happy.

259
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:01,200
But I'm a little reluctant to leave.

260
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:08,310
There's nothing to be reluctant about.

261
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:09,340
Young people

262
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:11,970
should stride forward.

263
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,720
Don't overthink things.

264
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,960
Do not act like an old madam.

265
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,390
What do you mean?

266
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:20,080
Can't you just keep quiet?

267
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:24,960
Miyu.

268
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,000
I heard

269
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:28,260
that Mr. Ji

270
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,000
was under immense pressure

271
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:32,250
to recommend
a forewoman of the HSKP Department

272
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:33,690
to be the lobby manager.

273
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:36,120
I had a feeling it was you.

274
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,640
Congratulations.

275
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:40,360
Getting promoted under Mr. Ji

276
00:12:40,380 --> 00:12:42,770
fully proves your capability.

277
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:45,780
Thank you, Chairman Wei.

278
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,390
Aunt Wanjun.

279
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,200
Thank you, Daniel.

280
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,240
I'll leave it to you.

281
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:52,220
I'll be leaving now.

282
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:52,910
Okay.

283
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:54,470
