Lu Xiaoyan,

564
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,640
please help this guest first.

565
00:26:57,750 --> 00:26:59,110
She was already here.

566
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,590
If you miss your number,
you have to line up again.

567
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:03,260
We all follow the rules

568
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:04,740
fairly and justly.

569
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:07,750
Ms. Xu.

570
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,550
You don't know the reception work.

571
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:11,160
So, could you please
stay out of this matter?

572
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,160
I think you should

573
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:14,090
take care of the guests over there.

574
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:19,000
Do you have any tissues?

575
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:20,360
Enjoy your stay.

576
00:27:24,050 --> 00:27:24,770
Thank you.

577
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,000
Cleaners, please come to the lobby.

578
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,040
Hello.

579
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:36,080
She's your superior after all.

580
00:27:36,340 --> 00:27:37,820
Why make her do that?

581
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,000
Come on.

582
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:41,920
Take some tissues.

583
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:42,400
Come on.

584
00:27:42,830 --> 00:27:44,560
Isn't that her old profession?

585
00:28:00,890 --> 00:28:01,960
You don't know the reception work.

586
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,590
So, could you please
stay out of this matter?

587
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:04,590
I think you should

588
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,520
take care of the guests over there.

589
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,750
Ms. Xu.

590
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,000
Ms. Sun.

591
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,640
It is you.

592
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:03,160
You're getting prettier.

593
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,680
I almost didn't recognize you.

594
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,750
Ms. Sun, I'm sorry.

595
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:07,310
I didn't have time to greet you.

596
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,920
I'm transferred to the lobby now

597
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:10,050
and become the lobby manager.

598
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:11,440
Congratulations.

599
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,750
Next time I come,

600
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:13,750
can I see you in the lobby

601
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:15,160
at a glance?

602
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:18,000
Ms. Sun, maybe not.

603
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,000
Why?

604
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,400
With Ms. Xu's promotion speed,

605
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:23,130
now she is the lobby manager,

606
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:24,160
but next time you come here,

607
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:26,760
she might be
the assistant of general manager.

608
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,200
Thank you for flattering me, Ms. Lu.

609
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,310
I will definitely work hard

610
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:31,570
and won't let you down.

611
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:34,070
I like your personality.

612
00:29:34,110 --> 00:29:35,510
You are brave and driven.

613
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:36,830
Keep it up.

614
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:38,400
I'll leave first.

615
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:38,920
Thank you.

616
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:39,350
Bye.

617
00:29:39,550 --> 00:29:40,350
Take care, Ms. Sun.

618
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:41,400
Ms. Sun, this way.

619
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:53,240
No.

620
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:55,260
I want you to pick me up after work.

621
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,200
I don't want to eat at home.

622
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:59,400
I have something important to tell you.

623
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:01,440
The baby is fine.

624
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:02,750
The baby is okay.

625
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,400
Ms. Lu, please sign here.

626
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:08,690
I don't care.

627
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:12,000
I want you to get off work early today
and pick me up.

628
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:12,920
At 5 o'clock.

629
00:30:16,310 --> 00:30:17,240
Love you, honey.

630
00:30:18,230 --> 00:30:19,040
See you later.

631
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:30,350
Miss.

632
00:30:30,730 --> 00:30:31,200
Hello.

633
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,960
We want to try yellow-feathered chicken.

634
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:35,640
Do you know which restaurant nearby
is the best?

635
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,000
You want to eat yellow-feathered chicken?

636
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,510
There are a few
good restaurants around here.

637
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:39,510
Please follow me.

638
00:30:39,650 --> 00:30:40,280
Okay.

639
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,720
This way, please.

640
00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:47,570
Look.

641
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:49,960
Go out this exit and turn right.

642
00:30:50,110 --> 00:30:51,110
Then at the intersection over there,

643
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:51,970
turn left.

644
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:55,030
You will see a restaurant
after walking about 100 meters.

645
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:55,960
Thank you, miss.

646
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:56,890
You're welcome.

647
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,590
Take care.

648
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:58,960
Honey.

649
00:31:14,290 --> 00:31:15,550
Who are you looking at?

650
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:16,550
Nothing.

651
00:31:17,010 --> 00:31:19,010
Just waiting for you to get off work.

652
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:23,640
Drive.

653
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:37,170
This is the first Mediterranean restaurant

654
00:31:37,170 --> 00:31:39,750
opened in China by Laura Garcia,

655
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:41,270
the famous Spanish chef.

656
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,550
Here,

657
00:31:43,670 --> 00:31:46,240
you can taste
the most authentic Mediterranean food

658
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:48,510
in a strong artistic atmosphere.

659
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,510
In Shanghai's spring,

660
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:53,510
this is a good choice
to gather with friends.

661
00:31:57,510 --> 00:31:58,710
My old friend is here.

662
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,510
Have a seat.

663
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:01,240
Okay.

664
00:32:03,590 --> 00:32:04,350
I knew

665
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,270
you'd only come to see me

666
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:07,600
under the guise of work.

667
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:18,640
On our opening day,

668
00:32:19,140 --> 00:32:21,580
I didn't know you were there.

669
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,230
Have I changed that much?

670
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:26,210
I recognized you at first glance.

671
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,960
It was mainly because
there were too many people that day.

672
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:30,510
Because of your video,

673
00:32:31,030 --> 00:32:32,270
many customers

674
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,590
came to our restaurant.

675
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:35,060
Good wine needs no bush.

676
00:32:35,090 --> 00:32:36,590
Your new signature dishes are

677
00:32:36,590 --> 00:32:38,160
truly amazing.

678
00:32:40,790 --> 00:32:42,390
When did you return to China?

679
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,830
Last November.

680
00:32:45,590 --> 00:32:47,000
You spent ten years abroad before.

681
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:47,960
As soon as you came back,

682
00:32:47,960 --> 00:32:50,690
you took over such a hot potato
like Purong Hotel.

683
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,850
I mainly wanted to save this place,

684
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,240
and also give my career

685
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,680
a happy ending.

686
00:32:56,270 --> 00:32:57,400
You are indeed loyal and righteous.

687
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,350
Not exactly.

688
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,570
Just acting on impulse.

689
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:07,620
It's been a while.

690
00:33:07,670 --> 00:33:09,850
Aren't you going to ask me how I've been?

691
00:33:09,850 --> 00:33:11,680
I don't think I have to ask.

692
00:33:12,090 --> 00:33:13,830
You are the head of Dianjiangchun team,

693
00:33:13,830 --> 00:33:16,960
an influencer brand
with tens of millions of followers.

694
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:20,180
Although I've achieved my small dream

695
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,510
and earned money,

696
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:24,750
I'm still alone.

697
00:33:25,410 --> 00:33:26,270
What about you,

698
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:27,360
Mr. Ji?

699
00:33:27,390 --> 00:33:28,920
Are you as miserable as I am?

700
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:30,950
Don't think too highly of me.

701
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,510
I'm still the same.

702
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:33,270
Then,

703
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,280
we're in the same situation.

704
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:44,400
So, how exactly does Ms. Jiang want to

705
00:33:44,850 --> 00:33:47,610
cooperate with Purong Hotel?

706
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:51,260
The famous Purong Hotel in Shanghai

707
00:33:51,260 --> 00:33:53,320
actually has many themes to explore.

708
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,000
It depends on how far Mr. Ji

709
00:33:56,020 --> 00:33:57,780
wants to go with me.

710
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,170
For a win-win cooperation,

711
00:33:59,170 --> 00:34:00,680
I will hold nothing back, of course.

712
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,550
Don't worry.

713
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,690
I'll fully cooperate with you.

714
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:05,790
Let's eat and talk.

715
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,160
The food here is delicious.

716
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:07,830
Give it a try.

717
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:08,670
Let's try it.

718
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,570
What's up, baby?

719
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:32,969
I don't have an appetite.

720
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,489
Is the baby bothering you?

721
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,550
I wonder who it was

722
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:40,179
staring at his ex-wife

723
00:34:40,210 --> 00:34:42,800
at the entrance of Purong Hotel today?

724
00:34:43,389 --> 00:34:44,270
What?

725
00:34:44,290 --> 00:34:45,480
Now that she's promoted to

726
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,730
lobby manager,

727
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,050
you're tempted again, aren't you?

728
00:34:48,050 --> 00:34:48,900
No, I'm not.

729
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:50,699
I mean,

730
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:52,730
you and the baby are

731
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:54,280
the only things in my world now.

732
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,320
I wouldn't think of anything else.

733
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:56,719
Spare me your sweet talk.

734
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:58,620
I'm involved in

735
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,480
your history of cheating, okay?

736
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:01,280
It's not fair for you to say that.

737
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,570
When have I ever lied to you?

738
00:35:02,570 --> 00:35:03,440
Nie Yucheng, your acting like this

739
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,840
makes me very insecure.

740
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,360
Okay, let me tell you some good news

741
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:10,020
to put your mind at ease, okay?

742
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:14,320
What good news could you possibly have?
Let's hear it.

743
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:16,180
I was promoted to vice president.

744
00:35:19,510 --> 00:35:22,920
Shouldn't you have been promoted

745
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,920
to vice president a long time ago?

746
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,800
Does that not satisfy you either?

747
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:28,930
Okay then, tell me.

748
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,330
Let me know what you want

749
00:35:30,350 --> 00:35:31,660
so I can satisfy you.

750
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:38,240
Sign the contract for the new house
next week.

751
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,360
Well, as for this...

752
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,210
Didn't you say there was no rush before?

753
00:35:44,210 --> 00:35:45,410
How is this not a rush?

754
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:47,960
Look how big my belly is.

755
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,280
I'm going to give birth soon.

756
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,630
Where will the child live when it's born?

757
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:52,800
The three of us live in one room
with your mom?

758
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,000
Is that appropriate?

759
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:56,920
Okay. Fine.

760
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,120
But the problem is that

761
00:35:58,120 --> 00:35:59,400
our family doesn't have

762
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,840
that much spare money.

763
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,880
We do.

764
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:04,280
Where did your millions in investments go?

765
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:07,710
I don't think we should use that money.

766
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:10,590
Nie Yucheng, what do you mean?

767
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:12,280
Why are you always making excuses?

768
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,230
Do you not love me and the baby?

769
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:13,670
No, no, no.

770
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:14,360
Tell the truth.

771
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:14,760
No.

772
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:17,320
Don't blow it out of proportion.
I love you.

773
00:36:22,190 --> 00:36:22,960
Fine.

774
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:24,480
I promise you then.

775
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:26,070
Really?

776
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:26,880
Really.

777
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:28,410
I guarantee that

778
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:31,070
the baby will live in a new house
upon birth.

779
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,710
Are you lying?

780
00:36:33,710 --> 00:36:34,760
I'm not lying.

781
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:36,290
When have I ever lied to you?

782
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,630
Are you happy?

783
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,280
You're happy now.

784
00:36:42,070 --> 00:36:42,960
Okay, okay, okay.

785
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,290
As long as you're happy.

786
00:36:48,810 --> 00:36:50,270
It must have been ten years

787
00:36:50,270 --> 00:36:51,620
since last time

788
00:36:52,010 --> 00:36:54,210
we walked side by side like this, right?

789
00:36:54,770 --> 00:36:55,920
Time flies.

790
00:36:58,030 --> 00:36:58,800
You know,

791
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:01,040
over the past ten years,

792
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:03,310
I've been having the same dream.

793
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:06,660
I dreamed of the day I left the house,

794
00:37:07,130 --> 00:37:08,630
dragging my luggage.

795
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,710
Back then,

796
00:37:14,530 --> 00:37:16,790
I always wanted to see the results first.

797
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:19,400
I was so impatient

798
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:20,670
and anxious.

799
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:25,840
And I left you so easily.

800
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:30,550
Ji Feng.

801
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:35,410
I'm sorry.

802
00:37:37,170 --> 00:37:38,770
You don't have to apologize.

803
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:41,680
We were both young back then.

804
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,480
I was just a hotel attendant.

805
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:46,260
I couldn't even see my own future,

806
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:48,800
let alone give you the life you wanted.

807
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:50,770
It was right for you to leave.

808
00:37:50,790 --> 00:37:52,050
At least after leaving me,

809
00:37:52,050 --> 00:37:53,780
you did what you wanted to do,

810
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,880
experienced a wider world,

811
00:37:56,430 --> 00:37:58,030
and became who you are today.

812
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:00,730
So you don't blame me anymore?

813
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,130
It's all in the past.

814
00:38:07,920 --> 00:38:08,550
Really.

815
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:10,630
Seeing how successful you are now,

816
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:12,280
I'm very happy for you.

817
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,000
Me too.

818
00:38:14,190 --> 00:38:16,850
You're still the same as
I knew you ten years ago.

819
00:38:17,590 --> 00:38:18,320
That's nice.

820
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:26,760
Here's to a pleasant cooperation ahead.

821
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,920
Yes, to a great cooperation.

822
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:48,000
I wish all the musicians

823
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,760
a successful performance tonight.

824
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:50,670
Just wait for

825
00:38:50,700 --> 00:38:52,150
a big surprise.

826
00:38:55,190 --> 00:38:56,500
Should we play a piece

827
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:57,920
for Miyu

828
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:58,760
to reward her?

829
00:38:58,760 --> 00:38:59,320
Let's play one piece for her.

830
00:38:59,320 --> 00:38:59,880
Okay.

831
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,480
Here we go.

832
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:38,420
Hello, Mr. Ji and Mr. Xue.

833
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:41,840
I just came to remind everyone

834
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,360
that tonight's performance

835
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:44,760
will last for a long time.

836
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,530
Take the time to rest for a while.

837
00:39:46,530 --> 00:39:47,570
No problem.

838
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:52,470
I'll leave the Western restaurant to you
tonight.

839
00:40:01,770 --> 00:40:02,870
Be careful, guys.

840
00:40:03,510 --> 00:40:04,970
A little lower over there.

841
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:08,320
How is it?

842
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,510
How do you feel after listening to it?

843
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,880
You really dare to think and act,

844
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:15,010
getting a group of seniors to perform.

845
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:19,280
I admire your courage.

846
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,190
Rui, are you being sarcastic?

847
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:21,840
No.

848
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:23,400
They played very well.

849
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,980
I was also shocked just now.

850
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:26,110
With a performance of this level,

851
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:28,760
the alumni association
will definitely be thrilled tonight.

852
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:30,260
It will give everyone a pleasant surprise.

853
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:31,360
Pleasant is fine,

854
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,710
but surprise is unnecessary.

855
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:34,320
After all, they are old.

856
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:37,650
We still need to be careful
with tonight's performance.

857
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:39,670
Have the logistics team
keep a close eye on things,

858
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,480
and prepare various contingency plans
just in case.

859
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:43,000
Okay, I'll go check.

860
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:43,630
Okay.

861
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:59,260
[Purong Hotel]

862
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:06,400
Why does she keep running

863
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:08,030
to the Western restaurant today?

864
00:41:08,030 --> 00:41:09,110
That goes without saying.

865
00:41:09,110 --> 00:41:10,240
She went to show off.

866
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,840
There's a performance
at the Western restaurant tonight.

867
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,370
She got transferred there.

868
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:17,840
Alright.

869
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:19,670
She's just a cleaner from
the HSKP Department.

870
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:20,880
What's there to envy?

871
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:22,190
Stop talking about her all day

872
00:41:22,190 --> 00:41:23,390
and making her a star.

873
00:41:26,520 --> 00:41:32,350
[60th Anniversary of
Lussia University Alumni Association]

874
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:45,840
Ming.

875
00:41:46,250 --> 00:41:47,520
Eat slowly.

876
00:41:47,670 --> 00:41:48,480
Don't eat too much.

877
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:50,150
You have a performance tonight.

878
00:41:50,150 --> 00:41:51,880
A full stomach gives me energy.

879
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:00,840
See, what did I tell you?

880
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:04,710
Ming.

881
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:06,640
What's wrong?

882
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:11,070
How is it?

883
00:42:13,150 --> 00:42:14,110
It's stuck.

884
00:42:14,110 --> 00:42:14,670
Is it?

885
00:42:14,670 --> 00:42:15,590
What's wrong? What's wrong?

886
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,840
M-Maybe it's stuck?

887
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,770
Choking on food.
